Class WrapperScheduledExecutorService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.restlet.engine.util.WrapperScheduledExecutorService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class WrapperScheduledExecutorService
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.ScheduledExecutorService
    Wrapper of a ScheduledExecutorService instance, to prevent manipulation of the actual service.

    Jerome Louvel
